Description:
Previous day, the King Koopa (alias Bowser) and his brother lost the battle against our plumbers, Mario and Luigi. Thus, they’ve managed to rescue Princess Peach, who then immediately undid the spell and returned the Mushroom People to their normal selves. The kingdom is saved!

However, the only thing that worried them a little bit is that no rest for the wicked. Nonetheless, the two guys fell deep asleep and shortly a plumber, who is almost similar to them, woke them up on the outer location of the Mushroom Kingdom. It was Super Kevin (also known as Kevin Mario), their dream brother! After that, Kevin suddenly heard two familiar evil laughing voices along with Princess Peach’s screaming from the further castle. Quickly looking sideways he found a paper on the grass by Mario and Luigi:

“Hey! Me and my bro had kidnapped Princess Peach again. She is in my castle and you can’t do anything to rescue her! HAHAHAHAHA!

P.S. Bowser’s brother”

